1. Extended FolderLoadThread class to handle specific scenario (davmail.imapEnableKeepalive option) of loading folder in separate thread 
2. Moved FolderLoadThread class to separate file: created separate file for FolderLoadThread class instead of having it in ImapConnection.java file
3. Introduced handling of davmail.imapEnableKeepalive parameter to make application more customizable/configurable 
4. Added logging for FolderLoad operation
5. Added exception handling for Folder Loading